    We've also got a little message from recruitment:<br />
    Here's the list of roles we're currently recruiting for in Australia.
    Please reach out to our recruitment team if you have any questions on our priority roles!<br /><br />

    <b>Sydney:</b><br />
    Consultant Developers<br />
    Lead Consultant Developer<br />
    Sales Operations Manager<br />
    Graduate Developers 2020 intake<br /><br />

    <b>Melbourne:</b><br />
    Consultant Developers<br />
    Data Engineers<br />
    Graduate Developers 2020 intake<br /><br />

    <b>Brisbane</b><br />
    Graduate Developers 2020 intake<br />
  </p>
  <p class="message">
    Cheers,<br />
    <%= ENV['EMAIL_SENDER_NAME'].split.first %>
  </p>
</body>
</html>